        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Pelage of Myoictis specimens from various localities: (a) Group 1 (no. 37); (b) Group 2 (no. 4); (c) Group 3 (no. 44); (d) Group 4 (no. 43); (e) Group 8 (no. 16); (f) Group 10 (no. 2); and (g) Group 11 (no. 9). (a) was photographed in the field and it shows fur loss on the back from handling at capture, (b–g) Museum skins. (a) at approximately the same magnification as (b–g)." ;
